page.title: 06Monday June 10th 1985
page.content: I was woken by my mum at 8.10 am. I got dressed and washed. I didn't have any breakfast. I went to school at 8.30 am. When the doors opened I put the chairs down in the classroom. At 9.00 am the bell rang. I changed for PE and went in the hall. At 10.15 am we had assembly. We sang songs about caterpillars. It was playtime at 10.40 am. We came in at 11.00 am. We did a maths project about the number of possible seating arrangements in our class. At 12.00 pm we had dinner. I had packed lunch. I had crisps, Cheddar biscuits and a drink. Then I went out to play. At 1.30 pm I copied out my maths project, then we had a story. We went home at 3.30 pm. I watched TV. I watched Dungeons and Dragons. I had supper, then went to bed at 9.05 pm.
